Email info@thedivemotel.com to book
Hope to see you soon!

node.text:
SWIM CLUB MEMBERSHIPS ARE OPEN TODAY! 
Prospective Swim Team Members, The Dive is happy to announce that we are opening up our first round of Annual Swim Club memberships! 
Passes this year will be $495, and will run through the end of 2021. Annual Memberships will include the following:
- Annual Members have early, exclusive access starting daily at 11 AM
- A 10% discount on food and beverages at all of our outlets on-site
- Admittance to our poolside events and special pool parties.
- Annual members receive a 50% discounted buddy pass

If you’re interested in joining the team, please inquire at info@thedivemotel.com. We will be taking inquiries on a first-come-first-serve basis, but don’t worry if you miss out on the first round! More Annual Memberships will be opening up soon!
